OL,9,     Fdepressed Wolfie threatens to jump
OL,10,     Foff the pub roof.
OL,11,G0340 Citizen Smith
OL,12,     FThe Big Job: Wolfie owes Harry
OL,13,     FFenning a hundred pounds for
OL,14,     Fdamaging the pool table in his
OL,15,     Fpub, so Harry devises a way Wolfie
OL,16,     Fcan work off the debt.
